{"tid":761210,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"【與Boy'z同年出道】SKY 5變4出歌賀十五周年","createTime":"2018-07-30T07:50:17.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-30T13:46:40.000Z","uid":160973,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"ff0b7ea63e9a9b3abf76bc9899b9cb68491b68ef","tid":761210,"uid":160973,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-30T07:50:17.000Z","msg":"SKY 03年出道，由潘卓楠（Gilbert）、嚴嘉駿（Moses）、林卓健（Kin）、趙耀邦（Bon）和梁俊邦（Bonald）五位男生組成，當時幾間唱片公司都有出男女組合，同年英皇以張致恆和關智斌組成的Boy&rsquo;z對撼。<br />\n<br />\nSKY出道短短兩年就解散，轉眼已經十五年，有傳Boy&rsquo;z正籌備音樂會；而SKY亦突然重組賀成軍十五周年，雖然當年隊長Gilbert未有加入，但四子日前推出新歌《趁今天有空》仲拍埋MV！<br />\n<br />\n曾經與傅珮嘉姊弟戀的Bonald，今年三月已經結婚，現職健身教練；十五年來，Kin就一直拍劇和做主持、Bong教跳舞、Moses就轉行做地產經紀。今次四缺一，是因為Gilbert想專心教小朋友游水，重組是因為他們在Bonald婚禮當晚重聚兼上台合唱，剛好前經理人在facebook live看到，就約他們傾紀念project。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://bit.ly/2Ot5D8w\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2Ot5D8w&d=tvKTabl%2B8AIuEaxwPSc4YRv1o3X72Fc8dbph17rWX2c%3D&h=f9cfc572\" target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/2Ot5D8w</a>"},{"pid":"981e4556e37d3795fbd7f26e71b13c18b61d9474","tid":761210,"uid":177856,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-30T08:42:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/30/164248_a2ea5f9eaed240804107be5b53b5a532.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F30%2F164248_a2ea5f9eaed240804107be5b53b5a532.png&h=09e67312&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"d692ef0d9eacdb54a07ac80eae92d1fb9698f152","tid":761210,"uid":65638,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-30T08:45:19.000Z","msg":"情投意合都要散～<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4df48baf9d599d5e46b7925275153c8508bbfcc6","tid":761210,"uid":88491,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d692ef0d9eacdb54a07ac80eae92d1fb9698f152","tid":761210,"uid":65638,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-30T08:45:19.000Z","msg":"情投意合都要散～<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-30T13:46:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 入黎前仲諗緊係邊隊"}]}